{"hash":"798f06f3f63af678fdce8791e3062eb4150a0ad4","data":{"post":{"id":"b447823bd0c8c70c05f43ab64ba5a60f","category":"알고리즘","sub_category":"Solution","title":"[Leetcode] First Bad Version","series_name":"","series_num":0,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/akasai/Algorithm-Solutions/master/Leetcode/leetcode-logo.png\"></p>\n<br>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/first-bad-version\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">First Bad Version</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-solve\"><a href=\"#how-to-solve\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>How To Solve</h2>\n<p>처음엔 단순히 반복문을 이용하여 풀었다.</p>\n<p>하지만 진행시간대로 반복문을 돌리면 <code class=\"language-text\">Timeout</code>이 발생한다.</p>\n<p>이를 해결하기 위해 이진탐색을 이용하여 접근했다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"solution\"><a href=\"#solution\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Solution</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token doc-comment comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"token keyword\">@param</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>function<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> isBadVersion()\n * <span class=\"token keyword\">@return</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>function<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">solution</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">isBadVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token doc-comment comment\">/**\n     * <span class=\"token keyword\">@param</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>integer<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token parameter\">n</span> Total versions\n     * <span class=\"token keyword\">@return</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>integer<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> The first bad version\n     */</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">n</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> left <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> right <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> n\n      \n      <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>left <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> mid <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>left <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">isBadVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          right <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> mid    \n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          left <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> mid <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> left\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"reference\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Reference</h2>\n<span class=\"reference\">\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/akasai/Algorithm-Solutions/blob/master/Leetcode/Solution/11.First_Bad_Version.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github</a></p>\n</span>\n","tags":[{"title":"Algorithm","path":"/tag/Algorithm/"},{"title":"Leetcode","path":"/tag/Leetcode/"},{"title":"Javascript","path":"/tag/Javascript/"}],"date":"10월 05 월, 2020","update_date":"10월 05 월, 2020","timeToRead":1,"headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"How To Solve","anchor":"#how-to-solve"},{"depth":2,"value":"Solution","anchor":"#solution"},{"depth":2,"value":"Reference","anchor":"#reference"}]},"related":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Majority Element","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-majority-element/","date":"2020.10.20"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Sliding Window Maximum","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-sliding-window-maximum/","date":"2020.10.19"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Count And Say","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-count-and-say/","date":"2020.10.14"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Add Two Numbers","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-add-two-numbers/","date":"2020.10.13"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Merge Two Binary Tree","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solv